summary: Now that I’ve had some time to digest that little teaser... Watching Sansa Stark say those words, giving her home that she...
body:
Now that I’ve had some time to digest that little teaser…

Watching Sansa Stark say those words, giving her home that she fought so hard for to a foreign queen, FUCKING HURTS.  Like my heart ACHES for her.  

I am so here for the drama that is going to unfold come season 8.  All that angst and tension and pining and high-stakes political scheming. 

Also, Jon you better fucking make things right and never hurt Sansa again.  And make sure you give her lots of babies!!

Just him, running around winterfell, playing in snow.
